"列出待更新的 App Store 应用"
,
"en"
:
"List pending app updates from the App Store"
}
,
"--accurate"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用更精确但较慢的检测逻辑，会为每个查询的应用启动并取消一次下载，可能触发下载次数限制，且会为无法下载的应用弹出对话框"
,
"en"
:
"Use accurate, slower logic that starts then cancels a download for each queried app, which can exceed download limits & which will open dialogs for undownloadable apps"
}
}
,
"--accurate-ignore-unknown-apps"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用 --accurate 的检测逻辑，但会忽略 App Store 中未知的应用"
,
"en"
:
"Use --accurate logic, but ignore apps that are unknown to the App Store"
}
}
,
"--inaccurate"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用不精确但更快的检测逻辑，避免弹出对话框，并忽略 App Store 中未知的应用"
,
"en"
:
"Use inaccurate, faster logic that avoids dialogs & that ignores apps that are unknown to the App Store"
}
}
,
"--verbose"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出 App Store 中未知应用 ID 的警告信息"
,
"en"
:
"Output warnings about app IDs unknown to the App Store"
}
}
,
